Package: ssh-bw
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
         python3-cryptography,
         openssh-client
Suggests: bitwarden-cli
Description: Sync local SSH key pairs with a Bitwarden vault
  Scans ~/.ssh for SSH key pairs and synchronises them with a
  Bitwarden vault. Supports importing new keys, updating existing
  entries, listing/outputting SSH and PGP items, and deleting
  records. Credentials can be persisted via the OS keyring or an
  encrypted file (PBKDF2 + Fernet).
